**Summary:** This documentation describes the Amplitude to Extole event streaming destination integration that sends real-time user behavior events from Amplitude to Extole's Customer-Led Growth platform to trigger advocacy campaigns, refer-a-friend programs, and customer activation initiatives. The integration requires mapping Amplitude user_id to email addresses in Extole, uses access tokens for authentication, and supports event filtering with a 2MB request size limit.

